				\begin{document}$${{\rm{NH}}}_{4}^{+}$$\end{document}NH4+, enzymes activities, expression analysis, chlorophylls, and gas interchange were performed after two weeks of panicle initiation (December, grain filling stage). Measurements about yielding were performed at the end of the life cycle.

